Billing Module Front-End (Points)
1) Page Header

Title: Billing

Subtitle: Manage invoices, payments, and billing reports

Right actions:

Primary: Generate Invoices (bulk from approved shifts)

Secondary: New Manual Invoice

Optional: Record Payment, Export

2) Top Filters Row (sticky)

Date range picker: Today / Week / Month / Custom

Status: Draft / Sent / Unpaid / Partially Paid / Paid / Overdue / Voided

Client dropdown (searchable)

Service type dropdown (optional)

Search input: invoice # / client name

3) KPI Cards Row (4 cards)

Ready to Invoice

$ total + count of approved-unbilled shifts

Click → opens bulk invoice wizard (pre-filtered)

Outstanding

$ unpaid balance + invoice count

Click → invoices filtered to unpaid

Overdue

$ overdue + invoice count

Click → overdue list

Paid This Month

$ paid + invoice count

Click → paid list

4) Work Queue Tabs (ops-driven)

Tabs above table:

Ready to Invoice (X)

Draft (X)

Unpaid (X)

Overdue (X)

All Invoices

Each tab loads the same invoice table with different filters.

